to-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612213</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"睇埋呢個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝各位手足<br />\n我愛你地每一個  下次會更好"},{"pid":"9c489aac1bd4607f0919db0676d248b4ee9ee0eb","tid":1610644,"uid":291007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"食雞？係咪101果場？<br />\n其實真係差少少食到雞，失敗就俾人話無用<br />\n成功必成攻略一仗，怪只怪哨兵不足，好運果邊完全唔知沙燕有手足<br />\n解決通訊問題，下仗就食雞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4287615de68534d6ab895cf6eb784a960d8d9698","tid":1610644,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c489aac1bd4607f0919db0676d248b4ee9ee0eb","tid":1610644,"uid":291007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"食雞？係咪101果場？<br />\n其實真係差少少食到雞，失敗就俾人話無用<br />\n成功必成攻略一仗，怪只怪哨兵不足，好運果邊完全唔知沙燕有手足<br />\n解決通訊問題，下仗就食雞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"係 如果當時有通訊好  一鼓作氣兩邊一齊沖<br />\n一定會成個局面大轉變  即使班狗開槍<br />\n我地都必會逼到佢地退   前提狗支援未到<br />\n下次如果又係我開頭  會再做好少少<br />\n<br />\n睇番影片 果時支援到左其實都要走<br />\n真正覺悟留係果度打狗既 我諗唔到二十個<br />\n再留會失去好多手足"}]}